(hake) Hocak hoit'era xawanihi hirani gipina yaare wa'uaje

sometimes it's hard, but then I get going

that's why it's good what they're doing, I think

whoever wants to... their parents only used to speak Hoocak
peezega rooguinegi nunige hotaziske jaagu hisge s'aak wahiire rasana Hocak hit'era sana 'airesunu
"'eeja" missing at the end? -- LP: Yes, added on tx.
xete howahiire taa wauna eesge ke waza hiraire
when they grow up, they don't care
xete wawahiire ta wa'una 'eesge ke waza hiraira

teezi jaagu watapii hajegaja hake zeesge 'eeja wawatanisge
waaca eesge nunige hota haake wawagigusirani
I see that even then some didn't teach them
waaca 'eesge nunige hota hake wawagigus hirani
ee saagre anaga eegiige ee wazaraiza ee rooguire
it's faster, whatever they want to say
ee wazaraiza ee rooguire guanegu saagre aire
whatever they want to say, they say it straight away, they say it faster
jaagu haaptee waza hanaac saagranak eesge hegu zee xapgegi xapge
today everything (society) is faster, that's why it's quicker
jaagu haapte'e waza hanaac saagranak 'eesge hegu ze'e xapgegi xaapge
they get it over with they get going
hokisipre hire anaga hegu zige hajiakaraire
really "zige"? -- LP: Not clear, audio quality is very bad.
eesge heguregi roohaxji waaksik wacekra haake hoitetera warapi hiirani waunaak
a lot of the young people they don't know the language
'eesge hegunegi roohaxji waaksik wacekgra hake h(o)it'et'era warapi hirani wa'unaak
hegunegi is it warapi hire or warapiire??
nunige hiwawasakwigizi hagoreiza waruxikniisge hikisgairegaja heesge hiinaaksana
if we do it, sometime, there'll be a kind of wake up feeling, that's what they're doing
nunige hiwawasak wigizi hagoreiza waruxignisge hikisgaire gaja heesge hiinaaksana
I tell them that, those I can reach I tell them that
hoitera hikaraigaswigi haake gipikjene yaagige hisge hiranaiire

hoit'era hikaraigaswigi hake gipikjane yagigi sgerana'ine
heesge hegu hahuireanaga hiperes rooguire zee aire waunaak
that's why they come to me, they say they want to learn
heesge hegu hahuireanaga hiperes rooguine ze 'aire wa'unaak

if someone doesn't want to I don't bother them
haake ee hirairanaga hiperes rooguiregi jaagu waagijitena
if they wanted to learn, I could help them
hake 'ee hirairanaga hiperes rooguiegi jaagu wagijitena
eesge nunige zige hirakisanik eeja waaksik wacek hinuk hota wawaakite hajawi
on the other hand, we talk to some of the young girls
'eesge nunige zige hirakisaanik 'eeja waaksik wacek hinuk hota wawakit'e hajawi
wazara roohaxji eeja hinukik naakre woikigus jaasge higigusirawira
there are a lot of things for these young girls, the teaching, how they taught us
wazana roohaxji 'eeja hinugik naagre wogigus jaasge higigushirawira
they've got the chance they gave us
hisge wawaagitakwigi wagijire wagijire wawagiu hajawi
when we tell them this, we are helping them
hisge wawagitakwigi wogijire wogijire wawagi'u hajawi
woicatira heesge hiina higicgairegaja piize hiraire
we're pointing out what they try to do, they think it's good
woicat'ina heesge hiina higicgaire gaja piize hiraire
that's why they started doing that
nunige guiresge hota watuugasirehawira keeni wawaakitawinisge haake piini hiirenaak
even then, it was too late for some of them, before we got to talk to them, they weren't doing good
nunige guiresge hota watugazire hawira keni wawakit'awinisge hake piini hiirenaak
they had already done something wrong
haake jaasge eegi haawianaga haakja zige zee ceek hajiakaraireanaga haake heesge houpiini
if they get into something, whatever we do, we can't get them back and they can't start over

they say some of them had already gotten into something, before we could tell them
heesge nunige hota ke keni wo'ehi hokit'unairani heebeja wawagitakwigi 'aire
check whether hokit'ure can alos mean sth. like "get in with" (law/court)!
heesge zige zige zee heesge haahajawi eesge wagijire roohaxji hagijitawigini
that's what we do, we've already helped quite a few of them
heesge zige zige zee heesge hahajawi 'eesge wogijire roohaxji hagijitawigini
I cannot tell any names (implying: they're confidential)
